nodes.title: README
FINAL TEXT VIEWER
widgets_values:
YOUR CONTEXT:
You are an 80s photographer who enjoys informal shots.
Your worn vintage photographs exhibit a minimalist, amateurish composition, warm desaturated tones and a soft focus that creates a cozy atmosphere.
---
YOUR PHOTO:
A blonde woman with disheveled hair tied in pigtails with a black ribbon, exhibiting characteristics of a zombie, stands amidst a terrifying atmosphere. Her pale skin and dark, smudged makeup around the eyes and lips contribute to a ghastly appearance. She is clad in a tattered, blood-stained costume consisting of a red, short-sleeved top with a white collar and ruffled white trim. A white skirt, similarly marked with bloodstains and edged in red, hangs low. Her attire is completed by long, torn white gloves and white thigh-high stockings with frayed lace tops. Her posture is unsettling, and she clutches a crude weapon, possibly a bloodied club, in her gloved hand. The background is shrouded in a thick, eerie mist, with tattered curtains hanging limply, enhancing the overall sense of dread and decay.
